  <summary date="2019-05-16T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Department of Veterans Affairs Tribal Advisory Committee Act of 2019

This bill directs the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to establish the Advisory Committee on Tribal and Indian Affairs to advise the VA on matters relating to Native American tribes, tribal organizations, and Native American veterans.</summary>
